WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.839
O‘zingizni Parch va Poseyning moliya bo‘limida tasavvur qiling.

00:00:03.839 --> 00:00:06.030
Siz yaqin oradagi buyurtmalarni ko‘rib chiqishni xohlaysiz,

00:00:06.030 --> 00:00:10.429
shunda bu mijozlarga schyot-faktura yuborilganligini tasdiqlay olasiz.

00:00:10.429 --> 00:00:12.855
Order By bandi buni bajarishda sizga buyurtmalarni sanasi bo‘yicha

00:00:12.855 --> 00:00:16.440
saralash usuli orqali sizga yordam beradi.

00:00:16.440 --> 00:00:20.274
Keling dastlab ma’lumotlar standart holda qanday tartiblanganini ko‘ramiz.

00:00:20.274 --> 00:00:24.379
Siz bu jadvalni standart holatda Account ID tomonidan tartiblanganini sezasiz.

00:00:24.379 --> 00:00:28.339
U 1001 dan boshlanadi va shu joyidan yuqorilab boradi.

00:00:28.339 --> 00:00:30.414
Keling siz ustunda ko‘ra oladigan buyurtmalar joylashtirilgan

00:00:30.414 --> 00:00:33.195
sanalarga asoslangan holda natijalarni o‘rnini,

00:00:33.195 --> 00:00:36.299
o‘zgartiruvchi Order By bandini qo‘shamiz.

00:00:36.299 --> 00:00:40.734
Order By bandi From va Limit bandlari o‘rtasida boradi.

00:00:40.734 --> 00:00:42.585
Siz shu tartibda yozishingiz kerak,

00:00:42.585 --> 00:00:44.520
yoki so‘rovingiz ishlamaydi.

00:00:44.520 --> 00:00:48.119
Standart holda Order By a dan z ga, eng pastdan eng yuqoriga,

00:00:48.119 --> 00:00:51.090
yoki sanalar bilan ishlanganda eng yaqinidan

00:00:51.090 --> 00:00:53.049
eng uzog‘iga boradi.

00:00:53.049 --> 00:00:55.674
Bu ko‘tariluvchi tartib deb yuritiladi.

00:00:55.674 --> 00:00:58.179
Siz bu yerda nima bo‘layotganini sezasiz.

00:00:58.179 --> 00:00:59.865
Agar siz boshqa yo‘lda tartiblashni xohlasangiz,

00:00:59.865 --> 00:01:02.054
siz  tushuvchining qisqartmasi DESC ni

00:01:02.054 --> 00:01:06.280
Order By bandi oxiriga qo‘shamiz.

00:01:06.280 --> 00:01:08.400
Bu bizni 10 eng yaqin buyurtmalarni,

00:01:08.400 --> 00:01:10.620
ko‘rsatadigan ma’lumotlar bazasiga,

00:01:10.620 --> 00:01:12.240
olib borishni ta’minlaydi.

